descriptionHtml:
This tweak changes her hair, as well has skin tone. And some very minor changes to facial structure to make a, In my opinion, better Brelyna without losing her original artstyle.

Installation:
Place the esp in your data folder and activate it in NMM or through the Skyrim Launcher.

Uninstallation:
Deactivate the esp first, then delete it from the data folder.

Credits:
Mod Made by me, Kevlo.
Screenshots taken by ColateralDamage.
author: Kevlo
